Usage: qvs-installer <option> [content, content, ...]
Option:
        -h/--help:       show this help.
        -i/--install:    install contents. (default option)
        -u/--uninstall:  uninstall contents.
Content:
        vs64:   vapoursynth 64-bit.
        avs32:  avisynth 32-bit.
        pfm:    pismo file mount for avsf 64-bit and 32-bit.
        lav:    lavfilters 64-bit and 32-bit.
        media:  mediainfo/copypath contextmenu.
        vsedit-recovery:    delete file vsedit.config.
        vsedit-template:    set template of vsedit.
